age = int(input("Enter your age: ")) #asks the user to input their age and saves this under "age"
isAdult = age >= 18 #Checks to see if the age is above 18. If it is, it makes "isAdult" true, if not it turns false.
print("It is " + str(isAdult) + " that you are an adult.") #A premade message that uses the isAdult string to tell the user if they are an adult or not.